story.text: Feeling sore from Yoga still. Stayed with Mitch the last couple days. What a genuinely good dude. Weird, but awesome.

I get to move back into my place today. Hooray! Going to NYC for 24 hours on Wednesday-Thursday. Thinking of cancelling, I am exhausted and have lots of work I need to do. We will see. Having a party on Thursday.
